---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="How It Works | Sell Your House Fast in Wichita KS"
  description="Selling your house to Jacob is simple: get an offer in 24 hours, pick your closing date, walk away with cash. No repairs, no fees, no hassle."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>How Selling to Jacob Works</h1>
      <p>Simple. Fast. No surprises.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="content-page">
      <h2>Step 1: Tell Us About Your Property</h2>
      <p>Call or text (316) 816-2983, or fill out the short form on this site. We'll ask a few basic questions about the property — address, condition, your situation. Takes about 5 minutes.</p>

      <h2>Step 2: We Assess and Make an Offer</h2>
      <p>We'll look at your property (sometimes in person, sometimes we can do it remotely) and make you a cash offer within 24 hours. The offer is based on real Wichita market data — not a random low-ball number.</p>

      <h2>Step 3: You Decide</h2>
      <p>No pressure. Take the offer or don't. If you want to think about it, that's fine. If you want to understand how we arrived at the number, Jacob will walk you through it.</p>

      <h2>Step 4: Pick Your Closing Date</h2>
      <p>If you accept, you choose the closing date. Need to close in 7 days? We can do that. Need 45 days to get things organized? That works too. We use a local Wichita title company and handle all the paperwork.</p>

      <h2>Step 5: Walk Away With Cash</h2>
      <p>On closing day, you sign the paperwork and walk away with your money. No repairs made. No cleaning done. No fees paid. Just done.</p>

      <h2>What You'll Never Deal With</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Agent commissions (typically 5-6% of the sale price)</li>
        <li>Repair requests from buyers</li>
        <li>Open houses and strangers walking through your home</li>
        <li>Deals falling through because the buyer's financing collapsed</li>
        <li>Months of waiting and uncertainty</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  <section class="cta-block">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Ready to Start?</h2>
      <p>Call Jacob today. No obligation, no pressure.</p>
      <a href="tel:3168162983" class="btn-dark">Call (316) 816-2983</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
